### Description

Hi 
the Editor control in MAUI is replacing the double quotes with invalid quotes the make the file invalid to parse as Json.
The char below  
<img width="166" alt="image" src="https://github.com/dotnet/maui/assets/9278908/02b01c5a-20ec-4a29-98fd-20cb6a299518">
is replaced with this before the word
<img width="166" alt="image" src="https://github.com/dotnet/maui/assets/9278908/fdbf7537-02c4-4fcb-97a9-b24c48a0742f">
and this after the word with quotes
<img width="167" alt="image" src="https://github.com/dotnet/maui/assets/9278908/f275da89-8911-4bfc-925a-2fe3c9de8a63">

that create a invalid json

### Steps to Reproduce

